concept.title: IEC 61850 Reality Modular AC UPS List

othermeta.name: shortdesc
othermeta.content: Lists IEC 61850 mappings and modular AC UPS communication modules for Reality modular AC UPS systems.

conbody.p: The default logical device (LD) for all IEC tags for Reality Modular AC UPS is “i61GMODACUPS_LD1”.

The IEC tag path format is LN$FC$DO$DA.
Logical node (LN)
Functional constraint (FC)
Data object (DO)
Data attribute (DA)
conbody.note: The modbus register listed in the table is the number from the system controller, it is not the same as the NMC modbus register.
